# ============================================================
# WhatsApp Business API (Meta) - Optional Feature
# ============================================================
# Get these from Meta Business Suite -> WhatsApp -> API Setup
# Required for WhatsApp gold rate updates feature
# Leave empty if not using WhatsApp integration

# Webhook verify token (create your own secure string)
